| 2 | `main.py:1454` in `run_loop_once()` | Reconciliation every 20 loops finds stale orders | **NO** |
| 3 | `main.py:2024` in `run_loop_once()` | Step 6c health check â€” slots missing entries | **YES** (already fixed) |

